sentences: Manuel Mota (born October 22, 1970) is a jazz guitarist from Lisbon, Portugal.
Although his interest was in blues rock, he turned to free improvisation and experimental music in the 1980s.
He has a degree in architecture and owns the record label Headlights.
I Wish I'd Never Met You (Headlights, 1999)
For Your Protection Why Don't You Just Paint Yourself Real Good Like an Indian (Headlights, 2001)
